{
  "texts": [
    "Other works rely on existing tools such as CoreNLP, OpenNLP and Gerbil.",
    "Analytical synthesisThis section aims to answer the research questions presented in Sect. 4.",
    "Answering these questions allows us to conclude this survey by giving a general picture of the current situation of the research related to EL, NER and NED.",
    "Answering these questions will also highlight open issues related to the field of EL that require further research.R1: After analysing the presented works, we conclude that the majority of the presented works aim to extract/recognise entities only (NER task).",
    "Disambiguation is only proposed by the most recent studies (the majority of them in 2018)."
  ]
}